data.description: Introducing a stunning 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with 2 living areas and 2 dining rooms, perfect for families or those who love to entertain. The extended driveway provides ample space for a boat and extra vehicles, while the loft offers a versatile gameroom or additional living space. The spacious master bedroom boasts an ensuite for added convenience and privacy. Enjoy the outdoors on the covered patio, perfect for relaxing and entertaining guests. This home is the epitome of luxury and comfort, offering ample space and modern amenities for a truly exceptional living experience.
